<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NVS E-SPORT</title>
<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
}
header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
}
header img {
  height: 50px;
}
.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: 28px;
  color: #22c55e;
}
.btn {
  background: #22c55e;
  padding: 12px 20px;
  border: none;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 16px;
}
.section {
  padding: 30px 20px;
}
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 10px;
}
.card {
  background: #111;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: center;
}
.card img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 10px;
}
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #777;
}
</style>
</head>
<body><header>
  <img src="logo.png" alt="NVS Logo">
</header><section class="hero">
  <h1>NVS E-SPORT</h1>
  <p>Time competitivo de Free Fire</p>
  <br>
  <a href="https://discord.gg/hHCvPdyw">
    <button class="btn">Entrar no Time</button>
  </a>
</section><section class="section">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;">Uniformes Oficiais</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="calca.jpg">
      <p>Calça NVS</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="moletom.jpg">
      <p>Moletom NVS</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="camisa-frente.jpg">
      <p>Camisa NVS</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="camisa-costas.jpg">
      <p>Costas</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section><section class="section">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;">Sobre</h2>
  <p style="text-align:center; color:#aaa;">
    Fundada em 2021, a NVS E-SPORT busca revelar novos talentos no cenário competitivo.
  </p>
</section><footer>
  © 2026 NVS E-SPORT
</footer></body>
</html>
